      "id": "PopularPost148456",
      "post_content": "*\"Can we activate its second ability more than once? Say for example, can I spend 6 colorless mana and have the guardian block 4 total creatures? \"*   \n   \nSure, there's no clause preventing you from activating the ability as many times as you have the mana for. The \"additional creatures\" do stack; it's not worded \"Luminous Guardian can block two creatures this turn\", or something similar.",
      "posted_by": "scumbling1",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost148456\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\"><i>\"Can we activate its second ability more than once? Say for example, can I spend 6 colorless mana and have the guardian block 4 total creatures? \"</i> <br/> <br/>Sure, there's no clause preventing you from activating the ability as many times as you have the mana for. The \"additional creatures\" do stack; it's not worded \"Luminous Guardian can block two creatures this turn\", or something similar.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '148456'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy3892\">scumbling1</span>\r\n                                (3/30/2011 7:45:33 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../